biotools.summary: The complete analysis of deep sequencing data from the DISSEQT paper is available at the collaborative science platform Synapse here. In order to view and download files you must create a Synapse account. (The scripts are also available in the examples folder for reference, but note that you will need a Synapse account to access the data files.)
